  "description": "Self-test fixture for single-name USD CDS pricing with two-step calibration. Pay-protection 5Y CDS at 100bp running spread on a synthetic ACME-CORP issuer, 10MM USD notional, ISDA NA convention. Exercises both the discount step (USD-OIS, with ois_compounding override) and the hazard step (ACME-HZD from 5 CDS par-spread quotes 1Y-10Y, against the calibrated discount curve). Closes the hazard calibration coverage gap on a single-name CDS instrument (the only prior hazard-step coverage was via CDX IG 46 / cds_option).",
