    "as_of": "2026-04-30",
    "source": "formula",
    "source_detail": "Self-test fixture: 5 CDS par-spread quotes (1Y/3Y/5Y/7Y/10Y, 60-150 bp rising term structure) calibrate the ACME-HZD hazard curve against a SOFR OIS-bootstrapped discount curve. Expected outputs captured from Finstack's own calibrate + CDS pricer round-trip. Round-trip stability: re-running the pipeline must reproduce these values within solver tolerance. Guards regressions in the hazard-step bootstrap, the CDS pricing kernel (premium leg + protection-leg integration), and the new two-step rates+credit calibration plumbing.",
    "captured_by": "claude",
    "captured_on": "2026-05-09",
    "last_reviewed_by": "claude",
    "last_reviewed_on": "2026-05-09",
